.TH CLAUDE-WIKI 1 "2026-06-20" "claude-wiki 0.9.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
claude-wiki \- installable hooks and CLI for a personal knowledge base
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B claude-wiki
.RI [ OPTIONS ]
.I COMMAND
.RI [ ARGS ]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B claude-wiki
captures Claude Code conversation context through hooks, then compiles daily
logs into a wiki of atomic articles stored in a knowledge base. It provides
commands to initialise repositories, compile logs, query the knowledge base,
lint articles, and manage the global registry.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.BR \-h , " \-\-help"
Show the help message and exit.
.TP
.BR \-v , " \-\-version"
Show the version and exit.
.SH COMMANDS
.TP
.B init
Initialise a knowledge base for the current repo.
.TP
.B migrate
Check and migrate data when configured paths change.
.TP
.B compile
Compile daily logs into the knowledge base.
.TP
.B query
Ask a question and answer it from the knowledge base.
.TP
.B lint
Run health checks on the knowledge base.
.TP
.B register
Register an existing .claude-wiki.lock with the global index.
.TP
.B registry
Manage the global knowledge-base registry. Subcommands: list, show, remove, clean.
.TP
.B rename-catalog
Rename index.md to the repo-named catalog and rewrite wikilinks.
.TP
.B status
Diagnose repository health.
.SH ENVIRONMENT
.TP
.B CLAUDE_WIKI_PROJECT_DIR
Override the project directory used for path resolution.
.TP
.B CLAUDE_WIKI_DAILY_DIR
Override the daily log directory.
.TP
.B CLAUDE_WIKI_STATE_DIR
Override the machine-state directory.
.TP
.B CLAUDE_WIKI_CACHE_DIR
Override the cache directory.
.TP
.B CLAUDE_WIKI_DEBUG
When set, enable DEBUG-level logging output.
.SH FILES
.TP
.IR .claude-wiki.lock
Per-repo configuration marker and machine-managed config.
.TP
.IR .claude/settings.local.json
Repo-local Claude Code hook settings.
.TP
.IR ~/.claude/settings.json
Global Claude Code hook settings.
.TP
.IR .claude/knowledge/
Project-mode knowledge base.
.TP
.IR ~/.local/share/claude-wiki-vault/
User-mode knowledge base vault.
.TP
.IR ~/.local/state/claude-wiki/
Machine state such as compilation hashes and build logs.
.SH SEE ALSO
Project homepage: https://github.com/mrrobot0985/claude-wiki
